    "longBusinessSummary": "Hoa Binh Rubber Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the exploitation, acquisition, and processing of rubber in Vietnam and internationally. The company is involved in planting rubber, coffee, and cashew; and purchasing unprocessed raw agricultural products, including animal hair, not tanned skin, milk, vegetables, seeds, silk, wool, rubber, and other products. It also engages in wholesale of raw rubber, rubber wood, and processed rubber wood; harvesting services; road passenger and freight transport; rubber wood exploitation; real estate business; growing vegetables, beans, and flowers as well as fruit trees; planting of annual spice and other crops; afforestation activities; and construction of civil and industrial works. The company exports its products to Asia, Europe, the Americas, China, and Taiwan. Hoa Binh Rubber Joint Stock Company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Ba Ria, Vietnam.",
